*
* IRIX 6.5 USB Mass-Storage class driver "usbms" descriptive file.
* Install as /var/sysgen/master.d/usbms
*
* Flags (modelled on usbaudio_dd's "cso" — a USB class driver that DEPENDS
* on the usb framework — plus block-device support):
*   c : character device (usbms_open/close/read/write/ioctl)
*   b : block device     (usbms_strategy/size)
*   s : software driver  (no EDT hardware probe; we attach via the USB core)
*   o : loadable module  (as used by usbaudio_dd)
*
* DEPENDENCIES: usb  — ml(1M) loads the usb framework first and resolves the
* usb_* symbols (usb_driver_register, usb_bulk_trans_synch, ...) for us.
*
* SOFT (external major) is left "-" (dynamically assigned).
*
*  FLAG   PREFIX     SOFT  #DEV  DEPENDENCIES
cbso       usbms_     -     -     usb
$$$
